WEBVTT

00:00:59.459 --> 00:01:03.834
Batman era orfano;

00:01:03.834 --> 00:01:07.532
Lyra Belacqua in "La bussola d'oro" di Philip Pullman

00:01:07.532 --> 00:01:09.221
era stata data in affido;

00:01:09.221 --> 00:01:11.956
Jane Eyre, adottata;

00:01:11.956 --> 00:01:16.539
il James di Roald Dahl in "James e la pesca gigante";

00:01:16.539 --> 00:01:22.051
Matilda; Mosè -- Mosè!
(Risate)

00:01:22.051 --> 00:01:24.498
Mosè! --
(Risate)

00:01:24.498 --> 00:01:28.994
i ragazzi in "Amico o nemico" di Michael Morpurgo,

00:01:28.994 --> 00:01:32.810
Alem in "Refugee Boy" di Benjamin Zephaniah,